<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Gauge-Theory on Chen Kai Blog</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/gauge-theory/</link><description>Recent content in Gauge-Theory on Chen Kai Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Nov 2021 09:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/gauge-theory/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>微分几何（十二）：纤维丛、示性类与物理</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/differential-geometry/12-%E7%BA%A4%E7%BB%B4%E4%B8%9B%E4%B8%8E%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Tue, 23 Nov 2021 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.chenk.top/zh/differential-geometry/12-%E7%BA%A4%E7%BB%B4%E4%B8%9B%E4%B8%8E%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86/</guid><description>&lt;p>在整个系列中，我们从零开始构建了微分几何：流形、切空间、微分形式、积分、Riemann 度量、联络和曲率。贯穿始终的一个主题是&lt;strong>切丛&lt;/strong> &lt;span class="math-inline">$TM$&lt;/span>
——所有切空间粘合而成的单一几何对象。Levi-Civita 联络是微分 &lt;span class="math-inline">$TM$&lt;/span>
 截面（即向量场）的规则，Riemann 曲率张量度量这种微分的不交换性。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>